profile:
Serving Spruce Grove, Stony Plain, and Parkland County, Queendom Cleaning provides residential and daytime commercial cleaning services.

At Queendom Cleaning, we really listen to our clients to identify exactly what is needed for us to make an impact. We aim to solve the messy home problem in an efficient, eco-friendly, and cost-friendly manner. 

We offer all types of home cleaning at any frequency. We also offer daytime and weekday building cleaning (condos and apartments common areas etc.), and office cleaning. 

You can choose your preferred way to pay: by the hour or by the job (we have some guidelines and will provide a quote). We also do free in-home estimates so you can show us around and we can get to know eachother!

We aim to make this process simple and are here to guide you. We are reliable, insured, bonded, and carry WCB - of course!
